tician from Himachal Pradesh\n*[[Virender Kashyap]], politician from [[Shimla (Lok Sabha constituency)|Shimla constituency]], Himachal Pradesh\n*[[Krishan Dutt Sultanpuri]], Politician from Himachal Pradesh\n*[[Dharmender Singh|Dharmender Singh Koli]], Politician from [[Aam Aadmi Party]], [[Delhi]]\n*[[Ramswaroop Koli|Ramswroop Koli]], Politician from [[Bharatiya Janata Party|BJP]], [[Rajasthan]]\n*[[Bahadur Singh Koli]], MP from [[Bharatpur (Lok Sabha constituency)|Bharatpur constituency]], Rajasthan\n*[[Ganga Ram Koli]], MP from [[Bayana (Lok Sabha constituency)|Bayana constituency]], Rajasthan\n*[[Ranjeeta Koli]], MP from Bharatpur constituency, Rajasthan\n\n== Notes and references ==\n'''Notes'''\n{{notelist}}\n\n'''References'''\n{{Reflist}}\n\n'''Bibliography'''\n{{refbegin}}\n*{{citation |title=Villages, Women, and the Success of Dairy Cooperatives in India: Making Place for Rural Development |first=Pratyusha |last=Basu |publisher=Cambria Press |year=2009 |isbn=9781604976250 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zJxY9IWzGewC}}\n*{{citation |title=The Internal Structure of the Nayar Caste |first=Christopher John |last=Fuller |journal=Journal of Anthropological Research |volume=31 |issue=4 |pages=283\u2013312 |date=Winter 1975 |jstor=3629883 |doi=10.1086/jar.31.4.3629883 }}\n*{{citation |title=India's Silent Revolution: The Rise of the Lower Castes in North India |first=Christophe |last=Jaffrelot |authorlink=Christophe Jaffrelot |edition=Reprinted |publisher=C. Hurst & Co. |year=2003 |isbn=9781850653981 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-rMW03l_gx0C&pg=PA181}}\n*{{citation |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EjORKo7maRUC&pg=PA168 |title=The Structure of Indian Society: Then and Now |last=Shah |first=Arvind M. |authorlink=Arvind Shah |year=2012 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-13619-770-3}}\n*{{citation |title=Caste and Democratic Politics In India |first=Ghanshyam |last=Shah |edition=Reprinted |publisher=Anthem Press |year=2004 |isbn=9781843310860 |url